                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"><span style="font-weight: bold">January 22 Update Notes</span>
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Gameplay</span>
<br />

<br />
Made slight adjustment to level 40+ mobs, so they have a chance to hit as often as you do. 
<br />

<br />
Changed several Heritage items from no trade to tradeable and attunable. 
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Tradeskills</span>
<br />

<br />
Corrected the description on the recipe for the Canvas Cap. The recipe description said that it was creating a Burlap Cap instead of a Canvas Cap. 
<br />

<br />
The recipe for the Ruckas Cap now requires a Generic Canvas Pattern and Canvas Padding. Also corrected the recipe's description. 
<br />

<br />
Corrected the description on the recipe for the broadcloth cap. The recipe said that it was creating a Burlap Cap instead of a Broadcloth Cap. 
<br />

<br />
Corrected the description on the recipe for the Cloth Cap. The recipe description said that it was creating a Burlap Cap instead of a Cloth Cap.
<br />
 
<br />
The recipe for Strengthened Leather Pants now requires a Generic Rough Linen Pattern and Strengthened Leather Harness. 
<br />

<br />
The recipe for Strengthened Leather Shoulder Pads now requires a Generic Rough Linen Pattern and Strengthened Cord. 
<br />

<br />
Corrected the description on the recipe for the Rough Linen Cap. The recipe description said that it was creating a Burlap Cap instead of a Rough Linen Cap. 
<br />

<br />
The recipe for Augmented Leather Pants will now look for a Generic Rough Linen Pattern. 
<br />

<br />
Corrected the description on the recipe for the Linen Cap. The recipe description said that it was creating a Burlap Cap instead of a Linen Cap. 
<br />

<br />
The recipe for Ebon Vanguard Spaulders now requires Generic Rough Linen Pattern and Rough Linen Padding. 
<br />

<br />
The recipe for the Cloth Cap now requires Generic Broadcloth Pattern and Broadcloth Padding. 
<br />

<br />
The recipe for Engraved Leather Boots and Engraved Leather Bracers will now look for a Generic Broadcloth Pattern. 
<br />

<br />
The recipe for Engraved Leather Pants now requires Generic Broadcloth Pattern and Etched Harness. 
<br />

<br />
The recipe for Engraved Leather Shoulder Pads now requires Generic Broadcloth Pattern and Etched Cord. 
<br />

<br />
The recipes for the Rough Linen Cap and the Linen Cap now require a Generic Rough Linen Pattern and Rough Linen Padding. 
<br />

<br />
- The EverQuest II Team</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><span style="text-decoration: underline">Quote of the Week:</span> 
<br />
<span style="color: darkblue"><span style="font-style: italic">"Caution: Cape does not enable user to fly."</span>
<br />
-Batman Costume warning label</span>
